  "type": "mcq",
  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">A group of 202&nbsp;people went on an overnight camping trip, taking 60&nbsp;tents with them. Some of the tents held 2&nbsp;people each, and the rest held 4&nbsp;people each. Assuming all the tents were filled to capacity and every person got to sleep in a tent, exactly how many of the tents were 2-person tents?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
